Description_lang: While inside the Maw or Torghast, damaging an enemy establishes a Blood Link.Blood Link pulses every $t1 sec, dealing $s2 Shadow damage and healing you for $s3% of damage dealt. If your Blood Link would overheal you, it instead heals a nearby ally. Limit 1.
